Class NameLookup

  NameLookup
All Implemented Interfaces:

public class NameLookup
extends java.lang.Object
implements Lookup, java.io.Serializable

This class is a lookup that matches stock whose name starts with a given sequence of text, to be passed into the constructor when creating the instance of the lookup.
